{
  "stem": "26609.16",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Do I have to look there, or you stop for a while?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Excuse me, pardon?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Which names?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His parents, no, not at all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I tell you something else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I forgot about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "About the life in her place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She used to entertain people, because she was so very wealthy, and such a big farm.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Very wealthy, she was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The government [PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] used to assign people from war, [PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] like SS men or from Gestapo-- I don't know what he was-- always a person to stay with for a holiday, if they were not too well, with a family who had a big house, could give them a room, and food, and everything.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they assigned for her [PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] one-- I think he was SS-- very ugly person, in uniform, of course.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was in that room opposite her bedroom where her husband, when he came home, he was there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I can see it opposite her room.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was [PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] in the house, not as a maid, but [PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] to care for the children.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When he came, [PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] he left for the night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was very dirty, terribly dirty.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He used to spit on the floor-- polished beautiful-- it was a beautiful home, polished always-- to spit on the floor or even to clean his nose on the floor.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] I couldn't take it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] Then he put out his boots for the night for me to clean them for him.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "For him, I was a forced labor girl, a girl who should do anything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "As he came from such a high rank, SS man, whatever he was, I should clean his boots.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
